Monopoly.Tiles

  • Packages that use Monopoly.Tiles 
    Package Description
    Monopoly  
    Monopoly.Tiles  
  • Classes in Monopoly.Tiles used by Monopoly 
    Class and Description
    OwnableTile
    An extension of the Tile class, which has fields and methods for colored sets, railroads, and utilities
    PropertyTile
    The PropertyTile is an subclass of Tile.
    RailroadTile
    The RailRoad class is an extension of Tile, with a unique algorithm to get rent based on ownership of other railroads
    Tile
    The Tile class is the superclass for all the squares on a Monopoly game board.
    Tile.TileType
    Enumeration used to express the type of tile the current *Tile object refers to
    UtilityTile
    The UtilityTile class is a subclass of Tile which has specific algorithms for getting rent amounts.
